{
  "stem": "23774.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sure enough, he left, contact some people in Winnipeg, and right away we get a letter from Canada to-- to Italy that they remember my father when he was alive, and they remember my mother.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're going to make a permit for us to come to Canada.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that was Yehudi Antilov's father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a farm in St.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Vital.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my [INAUDIBLE] from Winnipeg went to him and they told him the story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he made an affidavit to-- for us to come to work on his farm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, when I was in Italy, they said that a farmer can emigrate very easily to Italy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to school, to agricultural school, in Italy for over a year to get a certificate that-- I still have it-- to get a certificate that I'm a-- that I know how to farm.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, we came to Winnipeg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First-- it first took two years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the north, called Trani [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And around Trani, that place, there was the Adriatic Sea.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the Adriatic Sea, there were the Fascists' summer homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the Fascists were destroyed, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so the DP camps were in their place there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But again, you live in one room, because in that Trani camp, at that time, it was like a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were better than 2,500 people coming and going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were younger people that they were brought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were there a week, a month, two months, on a boat into Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I did not have any problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After one year, I spoke Italian perfect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to dress like they do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to go out with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
